{"type":"message","id":"bbd49e67","parentId":"44b856de","timestamp":"2026-02-15T18:43:15.520Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-02-15 20:43 GMT+2] OPERATION: MASTER PROTOCOL SYNCHRONIZATION.\n\n1.  **Read Current State:**\n    *   Read `docs_archive/MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`.\n    *   Read `docs/ACTIVE_CONTEXT.json` (to get latest fleet/tech status).\n\n2.  **Synthesize New Rules (from recent chat):**\n    *   *OODA Loop:* Mandatory Observe-Orient-Decide-Act for all tasks.\n    *   *Terminal Watchdog:* Read stderr/stdout, don't ignore errors.\n    *   *Polyglot:* Rust (PyO3) + Python + Shell architecture.\n    *   *DevOps 2.0:* `pre-commit` hooks, `hadolint`, `shellcheck`.\n    *   *Agentic Memory:* Vectorized logs via Redis Stack.\n    *   *Self-Perfection:* `SkillOrchestrator`, `ShadowMonitor`, `ReportingHook`.\n    *   *HFT 3.0:* `SharedMemory` instead of Redis for hot path (<0.01ms). `AdaptiveRateLimiter`. `orjson`.\n\n3.  **Rewrite `MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`:**\n    *   Structure:\n        1.  Core Philosophy (SACS-2026).\n        2.  Architecture (Multiprocessing, Polyglot, Shared Memory).\n        3.  Safety (Atomic Rollback, Spec-First, OODA).\n        4.  Performance (HFT Rules, Rust, Zero-Copy).\n        5.  Capabilities (40 Skills, Orchestrator).\n        6.  DevOps & CI/CD (GitHub Actions, Gitleaks, Dependabot).\n\n4.  **Verification:**\n    *   Ensure \"No LLM in Hot Path\" is bold.\n    *   Ensure \"Terminal Watchdog\" is explicit.\n\n5.  **Output:**\n    *   Summary of added sections.\n    *   Confirmation of write."}],"timestamp":1771180995518}}
